================================================================================
Third-party / vendored code
================================================================================

This repository contains vendored snapshots of upstream Canton Network
projects, each governed by their own license (see LICENSE files inside
the vendored directories):

- vendor/splice/
    Source: https://github.com/canton-network/splice
    License: vendor/splice/LICENSE
    Purpose: shared Daml/Splice utilities consumed by Canton-Dex during
    development. Snapshot of the main branch at the time of vendoring.

Token Standard V2 / CIP-0112 surface (`splice-api-token-*-v2` packages)
is included as compiled DAR artefacts under
`vendor/splice/token-standard/`; the source these were built from is in
the snapshot above.

